parameters.name: X-Fc-Account-Id
parameters.description: The ID of your Alibaba Cloud account.

parameters.name: X-Fc-Date
parameters.description: The time when the Function Compute API is called. The format is **EEE,d MMM yyyy HH:mm:ss GMT**.

parameters.name: limit
parameters.description: The maximum number of resources to return. Valid values: 1 to 100.

parameters.name: nextToken
parameters.description: The token that determines the start point of the query.
